here (packet framing, handshake, per-style LED index maps, and wire-remap
tables) was derived, for interoperability, from the reverse-engineering work in
the trrc-linux project:

    https://github.com/Lexonight1/thermalright-trcc-linux

This is an independent, clean-room reimplementation in Rust and is not affiliated
